primary_reference: Steviol, PubChem CID 452967; Steviol article, Wikipedia.

primary_reference: Leukotriene A4, PubChem CID 5280383; Leukotriene A4 article, PubChemLite.
notes: Unstable epoxyeicosanoid (LTA4), key precursor to leukotriene B4 and cysteinyl leukotrienes in the 5-LOX pathway.
Non-classic eicosanoid (5-oxo-ETE); highly potent chemoattractant for eosinophils and other leukocytes.
